      "content": "That makes sense. The \"coded language\" part is important. Can you actually write out a draft of a dialogue between three of these leaders—maybe a mayor, a local sheriff, and a businessman? I want to see how they'd actually phrase things during the meeting. Show me how they'd talk about the \"unrest\" without necessarily using slurs every second, but making it very clear what their actual views on the people causing the trouble are. Just give me a few paragraphs of them sitting in a private office discussing the \"problem\" in town.",
